A file manager for Windows (and Windows only). Written in C++ with WTL
as the gui library.

Nothing to see here yet. I just need revision control at the moment to
keep things in a (mostly) working state.

Ultimately it will look something like this:

+---------------------------------------------------------------------+
| Location bar (possibly with breadcrumbs)                            |
+----------+------------------+-------------------+-------------------+
|Favorites |Program Files     |7-Zip              |Microsoft Shared   |
| Documents|Users             |Common Files       |                   |
| Pictures |Windows           |Internet Explorer  |                   |
| Old Stuff|                  |                   |                   |
|          |                  |                   |                   |
|Drives    |                  |                   |                   |
| A:       |                  |                   |                   |
| C:       |                  |                   |                   |
| D:       |                  |                   |                   |
| \\Share  |                  |                   |                   |
|          |                  |                   |                   |
|          |                  |                   |                   |
|          |                  |                   |                   |
|          |                  |                   |                   |
|          |------------------+-------------------+-------------------|
|          | C:               | Program Files     | Common Files      |
|          +----------------------------------------------------------+
|          |<|                                                      |>|
+----------+----------------------------------------------------------+
